text: Kulachor in Jalalpur Jattan map Kulachor () is a town adjacent to Jalalpur Jattan in the district of Gujrat, Pakistan.http://www.dawn.com/news/131768/police-at-their-wits-end-in-chenab- bela It is situated about 16 kilometers in north east of Gujrat. It was built as a city by Chandragupta Maurya in 300 BC. ==References== Category:Villages in Gujrat District Category:Archaeological sites in Punjab, Pakistan Category:Maurya Empire
